Citation.sTitle: Determination and Correlation for Solubilities of Ofloxacin, Norfloxacin, Lomefloxacin, Ciprofloxacin, Pefloxacin, and Pipemidic Acid in 1-Octanol from (293.15 to 333.15) K
Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of ofloxacin, norfloxacin, lomefloxacin, ciprofloxacin, pefloxacin, and pipemidic acid in 1-octanol have been determined from (293.15 to 333.15) K by a static equilibrium method. The experimental data were correlated with the modified Apelblat equation.
